										</ul>
									</div>

									<ul class="card__meta">
										<li><span>Genre:</span> <a href="#">Action</a>
											<a href="#">Triler</a></li>
										<li><span>Release year:</span> 2017</li>
										<li><span>Running time:</span> 120 min</li>
										<li><span>Country:</span> <a href="#">USA</a> </li>
									</ul>

